gmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21fd4fb97dcd89f17c4a4bf0f705edf2a1351e5b","tid":246844,"uid":45301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T01:10:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=26625751&amp;utm_source=copy&amp;utm_campaign=ios&amp;utm_medium=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D26625751%26utm_source%3Dcopy%26utm_campaign%3Dios%26utm_medium%3Dshare&d=T8vHa4Omq%2F1xxkbvjwgdjp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=4ea4156a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=26625751&amp;utm_source=copy&amp;utm_campaign=ios&amp;utm_medium=share</a><br />\n試下入面方法，應該可以<br />\n我尋日又係咁</blockquote><br />\n唔該晒巴打，我試過都work。但會唔會因為轉左32bit而慢左架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我整完用左一日唔覺有咩分別<br />\n可能因為我都係睇動漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}